title: 关于星系附属的崩溃
author: RoMam
txt_content:
TO USERS: YES this is a BUG in the mod Galacticraft Core report it to them!

[20:33:12] [Client thread/WARN]: *  at sun.reflect.NativeMethodAccessorImpl.invoke(Unknown Source)...     
[20:33:12] [Client thread/WARN]: ****************************************     
[20:33:12] [Client thread/WARN]: ****************************************     
[20:33:12] [Client thread/WARN]: * A broken ore dictionary registration with name ingotMeteoricIron has occurred. It adds an item (type: class micdoodle8.mods.galacticraft.core.items.ItemMoon) which is currently unknown to the game registry. This dictionary item can only support a single value when registered with ores like this, and NO I am not going to turn this spam off. Just register your ore dictionary entries after the GameRegistry.
     安装了extra planets后就出现了 删除后可以正常启动 求大神给个不删mod的解决办法
